src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Numbers Midday' game
05 Nov 2019, 18:40 by The Associated Press
CRANSTON, R.I. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday afternoon's drawing of the Rhode Island Lottery's "Numbers Midday" game were:
1-7-3-1
(one, seven, three, one)
